NG0204:0: (10)@#// bltas chu mig ngogs sbas na /
NG0204:2: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:3: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang gang
NG0204:4: ba bzang po nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te le'u
NG0204:5: re dgu pa'o /// / de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0204:6: 'das gshin rje gshed pos gang ba bzang po gsang
NG0204:8: dam tshig dbang sgo thub pa'i bus //
NG0204:9: bla ma mnyes phyir yid 'thad dbul //
NG0204:10: mi don ma yin rang don du //
NG0204:11: bsgrub pa gong bzhin tshul bshams te //
NG0204:12: de rting man ngag 'di bzhin bya //
NG0204:13: a ka ru dang du ru ka / lug mig kar+sha pa na le //
NG0204:14: sngags ni 'di dag rab tu brjod //
NG0204:15: om dz+wa la ma ha dz+wa la /
NG0204:16: yag sha bag sha so su sdud de ba lam /
NG0204:18: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0204:19: sngon du bsnyen pa sum 'bum bya //
NG0204:20: lus bsrung sbyor ba 'di bzhin bya //
NG0204:21: dpung pa dag la btags gyur na //
NG0204:22: nad rnams thams cad byang bar 'gyur //
NG0204:23: de nas gsad pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0204:24: kar ni ka dang ba lu dang *//
NG0204:25: 'u su rdo dreg sha ka ra //
NG0204:26: ngang pa'i sgro la bskus nas kyang *//
NG0204:27: gzugs la dus drug mchod byas te //
NG0204:28: phyag byas bzlas pa byas gyur na //
NG0204:29: longs spyod dpag med thob par 'gyur /
NG0204:30: khrag dang nyung rgod rta mchin dang *//
NG0204:31: ba lang dag la bzlas byin na //
NG0204:32: rta bong la sogs rmigs zlum rnams //
NG0204:34: tsit+ta rus pa gyo mogs gsum //
NG0204:35: sngags 'di bzlas nas byin gyur na //
NG0204:36: om b+ha hu ri ri dza /
NG0204:37: ma g+ha la bag sha dza /
NG0204:38: ra ta ma ru ru dza /
NG0204:39: snying la shar shar ru dza /
NG0204:41: glang chen ba lang byin gyur na //
NG0204:43: bse dang ka ka ru la yang *//
NG0204:44: sngags de bzlas te byin gyur na //
NG0204:46: b+hi li ka dang a mar dang *//
NG0204:47: ru ram bu ram yang sbyar te ril bu bya //
NG0204:48: zla ba gzas zin dus su bya //
NG0204:49: ling+ga byas te gtums byas nas //
NG0204:50: chu mig nang du thod par gnan //
NG0204:52: bse zho btsan dug sbyar nas kyang *//
NG0204:53: gsang sngags gong ma bzlas byas nas //
NG0204:54: sha la reg pa'i ges [\[]gos [\]]la bsku //
NG0204:55: lhog pa dkar pos 'chi bar nges //
NG0204:57: yang na zha grum 'gro mi nus //
NG0204:58: dang por khas blangs bzhin du bya //
NG0204:59: phag pa spyang ki'i mche ba dang *//
NG0204:60: wa yi ril ma spyang rtug par //
NG0204:61: nyi ma gung ngam nam phyed na //
NG0204:62: sum 'bum bzlas te don po yi //
NG0204:65: srin rdo gdung chen sha ri ram //
NG0204:66: de rnams thod pa dum gsum du //
NG0204:68: sa'i khrag la sbyar la stsal //
NG0204:69: gong gi sngags bzlas lha rten sba //
NG0204:71: dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:72: srog gcod spu gri gnod sbyin gyi zla gsang las
NG0204:73: gang ba bzang po gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs
NG0204:75: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos /
NG0204:76: 'gal ba cham la dbab slad du //
NG0204:77: gdug pa klu yi zla gsang gsungs //
NG0204:78: nub phyogs pho brang rgya mtsho'i chu //
NG0204:79: ngo mtshar chu bo bzhi 'babs pa //
NG0204:80: rab tu mi srun klu yi gnas //
NG0204:81: de nyid dregs pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0204:82: bcom ldan gshin rje gshed po yis //
NG0204:83: lag na rdo rjer sku sprul te //
NG0204:84: lag na rdo rje thugs khros te //
NG0204:85: gser mig 'bar ba'i nga rgyal gyis //
NG0204:86: gdug pa'i klu rnams bred 'gyur te //
NG0204:87: rab tu mi srun klu rnams kyis //
NG0204:89: kye ma'o rdo rje gzugs mdzes pa //
NG0204:90: rab tu rngams pa'i rdo rje'i so //
NG0204:91: lcags mchu 'bar ba rab tu brjid //
NG0204:92: gser mig 'bar ba rab tu bgrad //
NG0204:93: mgo la yid bzhin nor bus brgyan //
NG0204:94: shes rab thabs ldan gshog pa brkyang *//
NG0204:95: thabs ldan sder mo rnam par gdengs //
NG0204:97: sku stod mchog gi g.yang gzhis brgyan //
NG0204:98: sku smad sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan //
NG0204:99: thod pa tshar gsum se ral kha //
NG0204:100: rtsal 'phags khyad par de bzhin mthong *//
NG0204:101: bdag cag rnams kyi dam tshig lha //
NG0204:102: drag po'i cha byad zla las rgyal //
NG0204:103: drag po chen po bka' bzhin bgyid //
NG0204:104: ces 'dzer zhing 'thon nas dam tshim smras te sku la 'khril lo //
NG0204:105: na du tra sa na d+h+ri pa la du+u sa ni gar si ti swa ha /
NG0204:106: de nas gser mig 'bar ba yis /
NG0204:107: nga rgyal chen po bstan te /
NG0204:108: dbang du bsdu phyir dam tshig phyag rgya bstan //
NG0204:109: dang po gnyis ni nang du bsnol //
NG0204:110: zla rnams rab tu brkyangs pa ste /
NG0204:111: khros pa'i nga rgyal 'di brjod do //
NG0204:112: ta ki dza de byi dzahde hu ya hu ya /
NG0204:113: hu lu hu lu pu ru te pu ru swa ha /
NG0204:114: zhes brjod nas che ba rgyun gyi ting 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0204:115: de nas rigs bzhi'i klu rnams la //
NG0204:116: rab tu che ba bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0204:117: nyid kyi gzhal yas khang chen po //
NG0204:118: rab tu brjod pa 'di nyid du //
NG0204:119: byol song rigs bzhi dang thabs cig tu 'dug pa'i gnas 'di lta ste /
NG0204:120: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus gnas 'bar //
NG0204:121: ri rab mchod rten gzugs 'dra la //
NG0204:122: bum pa yid bzhin lcang los brgyan //
NG0204:123: sbrul gnyis dar 'phyang ltar bus mdzes //
NG0204:124: rigs bzhi'i rgyan gyis rab tu bklubs //
NG0204:125: sgo bzhi ka brgyad rab tu ldan //
NG0204:126: de 'og sum gnyis rab tu mdzes //
NG0204:127: byol song longs spyod rab tu ldan //
NG0204:130: gser mig 'bar ba dang thabs cig tu bzhugs pa 'di lta ste /
NG0204:131: gzi brjid mtha' yas dung skyong dang *//
NG0204:132: gang po nor ldan la sogs dang *//
NG0204:133: dga' bo 'jog po ma dros dang *//
NG0204:134: rigs bzhi'i gtso bo klu brgyad de //
NG0204:135: sku la 'khril te rab tu gnas //
NG0204:136: gyad nor med la sogs pa'i rgyan //
NG0204:137: dar dpyangs ma dang pad+ma'i rgyan //
NG0204:138: gzi brjid ma dang dung can ma //
NG0204:139: klu mo rigs bzhi la sogs pa dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0204:140: de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos gnyen po sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:141: dgon pa dur khrod mtsho gling ngam //
NG0204:142: chu mig nags na gnas pa'i bar //
NG0204:144: dri spos sman gyis chag chag gdab //
NG0204:145: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud ldan //
NG0204:146: sgo bzhi rigs dang ldan pa bri //
NG0204:147: dbus su lag na rdo rje ste //
NG0204:148: 'khor lo bzhi la bya khyung bzhi //
NG0204:149: gru chad mchod pa'i bum pa bzhin //
NG0204:150: sman lnga spo lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0204:151: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0204:152: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0204:153: sgo la mchod pa'i gtor ma bzhi //
NG0204:154: b+ha ma ha sti bcas pa yi //
NG0204:155: sor mo lnga yi changs pa'i rjes //
NG0204:156: mkha' lding mchod pa'i rdzas su gzhag / de nas ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0204:157: dang po stong pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0204:158: gnyis pa snying rje 'byung ba dang *//
NG0204:159: gsum pa rgyu yi rnam pa las //
NG0204:160: bam gyi sa bon las byung ba'i //
NG0204:161: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus su ni //
NG0204:162: lam las ri rab rin chen bskyed //
NG0204:163: de steng khrom las ga ru da //
NG0204:164: rdo rje gshog pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0204:165: bya khyung rgyal po bzhi byung bas //
NG0204:166: dkar dang dmar dang ser dang ljang *//
NG0204:167: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du bsgom //
NG0204:168: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsings stengs su //
NG0204:169: ye shes mkha' lding stobs po che //
NG0204:171: dbu gsum rdo rje'i mchu khra la //
NG0204:172: ring la dmar zhing spyan yang dmar //
NG0204:173: zhal gdangs ral pa sprugs pa'i tshul //
NG0204:174: ye shes gshog gdengs sku yang shin tu g.yo //
NG0204:175: sku dang yan lag rin chen baidur+yar brgyan //
NG0204:176: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po 'khor lo phyar //
NG0204:177: bar pa lcags kyu tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0204:178: g.yon gyi dang pos rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NG0204:179: bar pa zhags pa tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0204:180: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:181: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po gzi brjid 'od po che //
NG0204:182: dbu gsum mdog dmar ral pa lcang lor 'khyil //
NG0204:183: zhal gdangs ye shes gshog pa chen po gdengs //
NG0204:184: sku dang ye shes yan lag me chen 'bar //
NG0204:185: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0204:186: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma rin po che //
NG0204:188: dang po rdo rje pad+ma phyar //
NG0204:189: bar ma zhags pa tha ma dbyug to bsnams //
NG0204:190: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:191: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po mi mgo can //
NG0204:192: dbu gsum mdog ser ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NG0204:193: yan lag rin chen sku las me chen 'bar //
NG0204:194: ye shes gshog pa rgya chen brkyang bskum mdzad //
NG0204:195: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rin chen 'bar //
NG0204:196: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma dpag bsam shing *//
NG0204:197: g.yon gyi dang po ye shes ral gri 'phyar //
NG0204:198: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0204:199: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0204:200: ye shes mkha' lding rlung gi shugs //
NG0204:201: dbu gsum mdog ljang ral pa 'khyil //
NG0204:202: sgra skad sna tshogs bzhad cing smin ma bskyod //
NG0204:203: yan lag rin chen brgyan pas sku 'bar ba //
NG0204:204: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po ral gri phyar //
NG0204:205: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma shing thog bi dza pu'u ra //
NG0204:206: g.yon gyi dang po 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0204:207: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0204:208: de rnams rtsa ba'i snying po khrom las bskyed //
NG0204:209: de bzhin spyan drang bzhugs gsol phyag bya dang *//
NG0204:210: mchod dang bstod dang bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0204:211: ba lim la sogs byed pa dang *//
NG0204:212: b+ha ma ha sti bcings pa yis //
NG0204:213: sor mo lnga yis bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0204:214: zan chang dkar gsum 'bru dang sman gyis mchod //
NG0204:215: om ra dza ma ha ga ru da /
NG0204:216: hum ba lim pu tsa ba lim ta kha hi /
NG0204:218: de nas sngags 'di rgyun du bzlas //
NG0204:219: od kam od kam khyung ka ra khyung ka ra /
NG0204:221: om badzra maha kro d+ha hum phat /
NG0204:222: sngags de rtsa ba rgyun du grangs //
NG0204:223: mkha' lding gso ba'i las byed na /
NG0204:224: bdag gam gzhan la gdug pas 'jigs //
NG0204:225: ga ru rgyal po mchod 'dod pas //
NG0204:226: gnas sam khang pa'i sgo ngos te //
NG0204:227: snum pa'i sa 'am bag zan la //
NG0204:228: ga ru da yi gzugs bcas te //
NG0204:229: ba lim la sogs pu tsa dang *//
NG0204:230: b+ha ma ha sti bcings pa yi //
NG0204:231: sor mo lnga yi pu tsa des //
NG0204:232: ga ru da nyid la ni dbus //
NG0204:233: snying po lnga po gang yang rung *//
NG0204:234: gcig gis sna drangs brjod rting la /
NG0204:235: ga ru da gnyis brjod nas kyang *//
NG0204:236: de rting pu dza rab tu brjod //
NG0204:237: thog mar om dang swa has dbul //
NG0204:238: 'di ltar gzhung bzhin byas nas ni //
NG0204:239: ka la sha tas zin pa la //
NG0204:240: grol bar 'gyur ba the tshom med //
NG0204:241: de nas gnyen po rigs bzhi la //
NG0204:242: mnyes pa'i bstod pa 'di yang gsungs //
NG0204:244: rig sngags bdag mo mthu stobs bdag po'i sku //
NG0204:245: e ma'o phyag gi mthil na rdo rje 'bar 'dra bas //
NG0204:246: zhal nas gsung skad bton pas khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0204:247: stong gsum drag tu g.yos pas klu chen pho mo 'dul //
NG0204:250: lcags kyu 'dab gshog chen po brkyang pas ni //
NG0204:251: gser gyi 'od 'phro rlung sgra drag po yis //
NG0204:252: rgya mtsho chen po kun tu brdabs pa yis //
NG0204:253: klu rgyal 'khor dang bcas pa zil gyi gnon //
NG0204:254: 'jigs byed gser gyi spyan rnon chen pos ni //
NG0204:255: tshangs pa chen po'i yul sa rtse nas gnon //
NG0204:256: gal te klu rnams dam las 'das gyur na //
NG0204:257: rgya mtsho'i snying po rgya mtsho'i lbu ba la //
NG0204:258: gshog pa chen po rgya mtshor byas nas ni //
NG0204:259: klu rnams thams cad dbang du bsdus nas ni //
NG0204:260: me yi snying po 'bar bas bsreg byas te //
NG0204:261: lus ni rul myag dri ni nga bar 'gyur //
NG0204:262: nad kyi rnam grangs mang pos 'debs pa dang *//
NG0204:263: lus la nad ngan sha bkra 'byung bar 'gyur //
NG0204:264: ga ru da tsa le tsa le hum phat /
NG0204:266: nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po tshangs pa'i bya //
NG0204:267: gser 'dab bya khyung ga ru da //
NG0204:268: drang srong 'khor gyi stobs po che //
NG0204:269: rigs gsum mgon po rdo rje rgyal //
NG0204:270: mnga' ris 'khor du klu yis bskor //
NG0204:271: rdo rje rnon po spu gri'i so gnyis gtsigs //
NG0204:272: gser gyi spyan gnyis khro gnyer can //
NG0204:273: thabs ldan rdo rje'i rwa gnyis brjid //
NG0204:274: yid bzhin nor bu gtsug na 'bar //
NG0204:275: lcags kyi mchu chen rno dbal gyis //
NG0204:276: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams spyi nas 'dren //
NG0204:277: rdo rje'i sder gshog brkyangs pa'i rlung mo ches //
NG0204:278: klu rgyal gdug pa dbang du sdud par mdzad //
NG0204:279: ces bstod de dbang du bsdu'o //
NG0204:280: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0204:281: gdug pa klu bsgrub kyi zla gsang gi skabs te le'u don gcig pa'o ///
NG0204:282: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos gdug pa klu sgrub 'di yang gsungs /
NG0204:283: mtsho 'gram chu mig shing gcig rkang *//
NG0204:284: nag rdzong mthug po dur khrod du //
NG0204:286: ba las byung ba'i rnam pa lnga //
NG0204:287: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga la byug / de nyid byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir //
NG0204:288: hum sa ma ya om gyi sngags //
NG0204:289: bya ba byed pas byin gyis brlab //
NG0204:290: bdag nyid chen por rab brtags te //
NG0204:291: thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0204:292: bdag nyid spyir bor sa dmigs te //
NG0204:293: bdag po bzhi yis dbang bskur ro //
NG0204:294: rdo rje'i sbu gur ma bsams te //
NG0204:295: g.yu bye'u sngon mos dbang bskur ro //
NG0204:296: tri dang ya bsam dregs pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0204:297: snying gar hum bskyed bdag dbang bskur //
NG0204:298: lte bar om yig gnyen por ro //
NG0204:299: de nas thig dang ri mo bri //
NG0204:301: gru chad sgo rnams de bzhin bri //
NG0204:302: lte ba mthing ka pad+ma dkar //
NG0204:303: mu khyud dmar po gru chad ljang *//
NG0204:304: sgo rnams ser por sgo 'bur rigs //
NG0204:305: de bzhin tshon rnams dgye bar @#//
NG0204:307: dbus su gnyen po dgod par bya //
NG0204:308: pad+ma brgyad la klu chen brgyad /
NG0204:309: rang rang rtsa ba'i sngags kyang bri //
NG0204:310: rtsibs mchan de ming bri bar bya //
NG0204:311: gru chad bzhi la klu mo bzhi //
NG0204:312: na sa phu+u na gru chad la //
NG0204:313: sgo 'bur ha sa tram ga rnams //
NG0204:314: shar nas bskor te rim par dgod //
NG0204:315: ces rgyun du bzlas pa'i yi ge dgu po 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:316: hum na ga ra dza sa ma ya che ge mo zhig tsit+ta dz+wa la zhes bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0204:317: zhag dgu bar du khrus byas te //
NG0204:318: zas rnams lnga ni spang bar bya //
NG0204:319: de nas grub pa'i rtags rnams ni //
NG0204:320: dngos su longs spyod tshogs rnams 'byung *//
NG0204:321: bar ni bal ldag thor pa 'byung *//
NG0204:322: de nyid mngon du gyur tshe'o //
NG0204:323: rig pa'i sham bu gdags par bya //
NG0204:324: smi ti gi ri las la gzud //
NG0204:325: ces don thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NG0204:326: dbang bskur bar bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0204:327: dar dkar gzhi ma btings nas ni //
NG0204:329: dkar po la sogs mu khyud ldan //
NG0204:330: dbus su dam tshig sa ha sa bon sa na 'dra min 'dug dgod //
NG0204:331: de nas yid 'ong bum pa la //
NG0204:332: bdun pa dgu pa'i ri mo bri //
NG0204:333: dge bsnyen gnyis por rab tu dmigs /
NG0204:334: kha dog tshang ba'i ras kyis bcings //
NG0204:335: rma bya 'om bu bra ma dang *//
NG0204:336: drag po'i rdzas la bdug par bya //
NG0204:337: ras la sogs pa'i gzungs thag gdags //
NG0204:338: sder gshog phyag rgya snying gar bstan //
NG0204:339: sman lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0204:340: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0204:341: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0204:342: om a hum na ga yu yu /
NG0204:343: na ga yu ru dz+wa la ni /
NG0204:344: na ga sa ma ya swa ha /
NG0204:345: dmigs pa'i yan lag gsum pa'i rgyu //
NG0204:346: yi ge rtsa gcig sprul par bshad //
NG0204:347: hum skyes bdag po gnyis nas sprul //
NG0204:348: yan lag yi ge rtsa gcig las //
NG0204:349: 'od zer sna tshogs bdud rtsir sprul //
NG0204:350: yi ge dmigs pa'i gnas lnga ru //
NG0204:351: bdud rtsi bum pa brtan par bya //
NG0204:352: mkha' lding rgyal po de nyid bsam //
NG0204:353: de nyid gtsang ma'i ras kyis dkris //
NG0204:354: gur gum sman nam chus bsres bkru //
NG0204:355: de bzhin ma smin zas rnams bza' //
NG0204:357: kye ma'o rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bdag / bdag gi dam tshig mngon dga' bas //
NG0204:359: khyod kyi dam tshig gtso lags kyi //
NG0204:360: longs spyod klu yi pho brang nas //
NG0204:361: rig pa'i rgyal pos dbang bskur cig / ces gsol to //
NG0204:362: nyon cig skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NG0204:363: longs spyod klu yi rigs kyis 'grub //
NG0204:364: pho brang yid 'ong mngon dga' nas //
NG0204:365: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams la //
NG0204:366: yid bzhin rin chen rab gnas pas //
NG0204:367: de ring khyod kyis bcang bar gyis //
NG0204:370: yang bar chad bsal ba'i phyir /
NG0204:371: rma byas brdeg cing gu gul bdug / ces gsungs so //
NG0204:372: snying po rigs bzhi dbu brgyan dang *//
NG0204:373: dar gyi con pan me tog phreng *//
NG0204:374: longs spyod tshogs kyi zhal zas dang *//
NG0204:375: rten gyi bum pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0204:376: de nas dam tshig rten 'brel gyi snying po 'di sbyin par bya'o //
NG0204:377: rigs ldan thogs med rgyug pa yi //
